# Workflow Engine systems?
co-ordinated MULTI steps for resources and processes
Eg: camunda, flowable, activiti

# social proof of technology you are introducing?
tweets etc, which companies are using it

# Standard
BPMN 2.0 maintianed by same company as UML, OMG

# Workflow systems?
- Execute tasks
- reacts to external events
- timers and timeouts and retries

Workflow definition -> Workflow Step(s)
Execute tasks from task queues

## Questions
- Who, what, when and why changed/created/deleted workflow step?
- Retrieve a component details of the workflow process?
- How to integrate it within an existing system?

